<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= poll.title %> | 여론조사</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/touchpad-poll.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="card shadow">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h1 class="h3 mb-0"><%= poll.title %></h1>
        <% if (poll.description) { %>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0"><%= poll.description %></p>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card-body">
       <form id="vote-form" data-poll-id="<%= poll._id %>">
        <!-- 간단한 옵션 목록으로 변경 -->
        <div class="mb-4">
          <p class="mb-3">아래 옵션 중 하나를 선택하여 투표하세요:</p>
          <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-3">
            <% poll.options.forEach(option => { %>
              <div class="col">
                <div class="option-card card h-100" data-option-id="<%= option._id %>">
                  <div class="card-body d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                    <h5 class="card-title mb-0 text-center"><%= option.text %></h5>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
        </div>
        
         <div class="selected-option mb-3">
        <small class="text-muted">원하는 옵션을 선택하면 강조 표시됩니다. 더블클릭으로 바로 투표할 수 있습니다.</small>
         <div class="alert alert-primary mt-2 d-none">
          선택: <span id="selected-option-text"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
          
          <input type="hidden" id="option-id-input" name="optionId">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" disabled>투표하기</button>
        </form>
        
        <div id="results-container" class="results-container d-none">
          <h4 class="mb-3">투표 결과</h4>
          <div id="results"></div>
          <p id="total-votes" class="mt-3 text-muted"></p>
          <button id="back-to-vote" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">다시 투표하기</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/touchpad-poll.js"></script>
</body>
</html>